data.description: Welcome to YOUR beautiful custom home built by Blair Weaver! It's located within the beautiful community of Pecan Grove Village which is only minutes away from the elementary school, shopping, restaurants, entertainment, and a quick drive to Lake Texoma. This home features everything that you've been looking for including a NEW roof, gutters, and exterior paint in the Spring of 2023! The upgrades include a new KitchenAid convection oven, Jenn-Air cooktop, under and over cabinet lighting, built-in cabinets in the living area, chandeliers, shutters throughout, wood flooring, granite countertops, floor-to-ceiling stone fireplace with hearth, beautiful backsplash, cabinet hardware, crown molding, built-in mini fridge and more. The upstairs bonus room is spacious and perfect for an office, game room, media room, or playroom! Do you LOVE to host family and friends? The backyard and shaded patio are ready for gatherings and cookouts! Come see it today!
